name: iShares Core Equity ETF Portfolio
longDescription: The investment objective of the Fund is to provide long-term capital growth. To achieve its investment objective the iShares ETFs in which the Fund invests are generally expected to employ indexing strategies that provide exposure to broad-based equity markets. The Fund is managed in accordance with a long-term strategic asset allocation of approximately 100% equity exposure.
